            "Q: asking about pm fasal vima yojona. A: it is a crop insurance scheme. if you want to do insurance against your cultivation viz., potato, masturd, sugarcane, boro rice ,then through this scheme you can do this.  required documents- adhar card, land record, bank details, valid phone number.   you can apply in your nearest common service center or bank or district agriculture office or block office.  this insurace schem covers the lose occurs due to natural calamities like, drought, heavy rainfall, hailstrom, insect and disease attack, cyclone etc.  to get the benefit of this schem you have to report the insurance company and you district agriculture office within 3 days of lose occur.",
