            "Q: asking about new govt schemes being implemented A: told him about the pradhan mantri fasal bima yojana- asked him to visit the district agricultural dept or atma office and take the form @ rs.1,miadi patta land papers, voter id,bank passbook along and meet the agricultural extension asst or block technology manager.and the last date for kharif crop insurance is on 31 august",
            "Q: asking about the pm kisan A: told him to visit nearby district agricultural office with proper documents like pan card , land documents , bank passbook etc",
            "Q: asking about pm fasal bima yojana, about pm kisan. A: suggested to visit district agriculture office or atma and contact agriculture extension assistant or block technology manager. the registration is done online with a fee of 1 rupee. carry land holding details, voter id, bank passbook along with you. last date is 31st august for kharif season. crops included in kharif season are sali paddy and black gram. insured amount for sali paddy is approximately rs.59,800 and blank gram is rs.38,000 if any natural calamities occur and damage the crop. for query regarding pm kisan visit block/ district agriculture office.",
            "Q: asking about pm man dhan yojana registration A: told him that the scheme will provide a monthly pension of rs.3000/-.  age eligibility for registration- 18 to 40 yrs. documents reqd. - land documnets (less than 2ha)                                        bank passbook                                       ifsc code                                       aadhaar                                       id proof contribution amount- on an average rs. 100 per month contribution                                                contribution amount varies as per age during registration.  visit the nearest community service centre along with proper documents.  csc add- csc id	vle name	address	phone no. as010700301	m. minisana singha	c/o lt sunamani singha, vill- binnakandi part-i, binnakandighat, cachar	 as010700306	n subrata singha	s/o n. madan babu singha, vill- sibpur pt-ii, p.o- kaptanpur, cachar	9401774305 as010700304	kandarpo nunia	s/o kedar nath nunia, vill- roberpui grant, p.o- binnakandi ghat, cachar, pin- 788130	9854751882",
            "Q: asking about pm kisan registration pm fasal bima yojana A: recommended to contact district agricultural office for further query of pm kisan.   for pmfby, submit documents like land documents, bank passbook, id proof and aadhar.  rs. 1 will be incurred for submission of form. crop insured are sali paddy, black gram, sugarcane and mustard.  last date of registration is 31st august 2019",
            "Q: asking about pm kisan man dhan yojana A: told him that it is a pension scheme under which an amount of rs 3000 will be deposited on monthly basis after attaining the age of 60 yrs. age of registration is 18 -40yrs documents required are land documents (less than 15 bigha),  bank pass book, bani ifsc code, spouse name & dob, aadhar card. monthly contribution will be required to pay from your end. ineligible condition- person who are inservice in any govt. or private sector or any local self govt. are not allowed to avail the scheme. visit nearest csc for registration",
            "Q: asking about pm kisan maan dhan yojna A: told him about pm kisan maan dhan yojna- rs.3000 will be given to the farmer who attains age of 60 years. the land holding should be below 15 bigha. the farmer should be of age 18-40 years old. a contribution has to be given per month varying from amount rs.55 to rs.200 depending upon the age. the registration is free and has to be done in common service centers of their respective block. documents that have to be carried are aadhaar card, bank passbook, land details. for further details contact vle of common service center",
            "Q: asking about the pm kisan maan dhan yojna A: told him about pm kisan maan dhan yojna- rs 3000 will be given to the farmer who attains age of 60 years .the land holding should be below 15 bigha. the farmer should be age of 18 to 40 years old.a contribution has to be given per month varying from amount rs 55 to 200 rs depending upon the age . the registration is free and has to be done in common service centres of their respective block.documents that have to be carried are aadhar card , bank ,passbook,land details . for further details contact vle of common service centre",
            "Q: asking about the subsidy regarding procurement of power tiller A: suggested to visit the department of agriculture and contact the agricultural development officer",
            "Q: asking about kcc loan procurement A: recommended to visit nearest nationalised bank and contact with agricultural field officer for proper procedure detailing. collect land documents, bank details and id proof.  a sum of rs 300000 is provided under kcc at 7% rate of interest. on timely reapymnet 3% subvention is given . so total rate of interest becomes 4% per annum.",
            "Q: asking about pm kisan maan dhan yojana. A: kcc loan , approach any nationalised bank along with documents viz. land documents, bank details , id proof and address proof. then contact agricultural field officer or branch manger for further process. loan avail is 3,00,00/- @7% rate of interest per annum. on timely payment interest will be subvened to 4% only.",
            "Q: asking about crop insurance (pm fasal bima yojana) A: kcc loan , approach any nationalised bank along with documents viz. land documents, bank details , id proof and address proof. then contact agricultural field officer or branch manger for further process. loan avail is 3,00,00/- @7% rate of interest per annum. on timely payment interest will be subvened to 4% only.",
            "Q: asking about kisan credit card A: kcc loan , approach any nationalised bank along with documents viz. land documents, bank details , id proof and address proof. then contact agricultural field officer or branch manger for further process. loan avail is 3,00,00/- @7% rate of interest per annum. on timely payment interest will be subvened to 4% only.",
            "Q: asking about  kisan credit card A: recommended to told him to visit nationalized bank to apply for kisan credit card",
