            "Q: asking about kisan loan (the farmer already took the loan but did not use) and kisan credit card. A: told him that since the loan was taken so it has to be repay to the bank with an interest of 4%. for further query contact the bank manager. to apply for kisan credit card documents required are voter id, pan card, bank passbook, land details.",
