            "Q: asking about agricultural credit for pm kisan beneficiaries A: kisan credit card(kcc)saturation drive for pm-kisan beneficiaries started from 10th february 2020 and will be carried out for a period of 15 days to enable universal access to concessional institutional credit, government of india has initiated a drive in mission mode for saturating all pm-kisan beneficiaries with kisan credit card (kcc). this will help all such farmers to get short term loan for crop & animal/fish rearing at a maximum interest of 4% on timely repayment.",
