            "Q: query regarding fish mortality due to oxygen depletion. A: critical stage(under, severe stress): immediately change the water @ 30% or give aeration using aerators.  *if there is no provision for replenishing the water or there is no chance for artificial aeration and if the water level is above 1m:  potassium permanganate @ 250 grams/ 0.1 ha and agitate the surface with bamboo.  *if the water level is low: reduce the stock to half and stop all feeds and fertilizers till the pond regains its healthy condition. to increase oxygen level- 1. oxy more tablet-20 tablet per bigha or 200 gram per bigha  2. oxy plus tablet-600 gm per acre.",
